   Search

Our Markets, Product and Services

   Saint-Gobain designs and delivers innovative and high performance
   solutions that improve our habitat and our daily lives.

Our major brands

   The diversity of our business and the strong awareness of our brands
   (ISOVER, PAM, Weber, Placo®, Gyproc, CertainTeed, Jewson, POINT.P,
   Lapeyre ...) allow us to be the reference of Habitat and industrial
   applications markets.

